<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>How it Works - Periodic Table: Interactive 3D</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS Play CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            corePlugins: {
                preflight: false,
            }
        }
    </script>
    <!-- Lucide Icons -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .content-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .safe-pt {
            padding-top: env(safe-area-inset-top);
        }

        .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }

        .no-scrollbar {
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .back-button {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-color: #2563eb;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="global-header"></div>

    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>How to Use the Interactive Table</h1>

            <p>Welcome! Here is how you can make the most of this interactive periodic table:</p>
            <h2>1. Selecting Elements</h2>
            <p>Simply click or tap on any element card in the main grid to open the detail view. You can also use the
                search bar to find elements by name, symbol, or atomic number.</p>
            <h2>2. 3D Visualizations</h2>
            <p>Each element features a 3D Bohr model and a Crystal Structure model. You can rotate and zoom these models
                to understand the physical arrangement of atoms and electrons.</p>
            <h2>3. Filtering</h2>
            <p>Use the "Filter by Group" dropdown to highlight specific categories of elements, such as Alkali Metals,
                Noble Gases, or Lanthanides.</p>
            <h2>4. Deep Linking</h2>
            <p>You can share a direct link to any element by copying the URL when the element detail is open. For
                example, <code>?element=Au</code> will take someone directly to Gold.</p>

        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Periodic Table Team. All rights reserved.
            <br>
            <a href="/" class="back-button">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
        <script src="/components/header.js"></script>
        <script>
            lucide.createIcons();
        </script>
</body>

</html>